{"tid":1608050,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"『正式宣佈』今日發生咩事都好，絕不割蓆","createTime":"2019-10-01T07:06:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T14:41:28.000Z","uid":169392,"like":445,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":91,"replies":[{"pid":"1c593593985af21f07245b9cb74950a16f32c1d6","tid":1608050,"uid":169392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T07:06:11.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家要一條心，絕不割蓆！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8312a8f8b1bf4b66d1943875e43fed8626306228","tid":1608050,"uid":49669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T07:08:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"528525c421374b8bdd7dc8d76c14752c9c7f4b12","tid":1608050,"uid":271434,"like":2,"dislike":18,"score":-16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T07:08:57.000Z","msg":"<strong>我以颱風風眼橫過比喻，預測閱兵期間香港唔會發生衝突</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">昨日警察不斷恐嚇大家十一唔好出，同埋有很多假消息話各地暴徒會燒商場，呢個奇怪現象同早幾日批不反對通知書後立即大搜捕完全不同，<span style=\"color: red;\">就係因為警察知道，十一當日唔可以捉人、唔可以出現血腥畫面，</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">但中共又唔容許有大量人上街反共反雜，所以先嚇定大家。<br />\n</span><br />\n現在就好似颱風風眼即將略過時候，警察瘋狂捉人，製造白色恐怖。<span style=\"color: red;\">風眼將會在閱兵期間橫過香港，忽然晴天萬里，到時候社會上一定太平無事，警察唔會拉人，大家可以放膽出街。</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">但要小心，當10月1日半夜過後，就有可能好似風眼過後，又出現狂風暴雨，</span>所以大家意見表達完結後，就盡快返歸，唔好戀戰。<br />\n<br />\n點解警察聽日閱兵期間唔捉人？<span style=\"color: gold;\">因為北大人唔想在世界各地直播閱兵期間，同時直播出現血腥鎮壓嘅場面，咁會落佢面，令雜種即時受到黨內外以及西方社會譴責，</span>所以十一閱兵嘅時候唔會清場鎮壓。<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">聽講呢個安排僅十一閱兵嘅時段限定！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1606271\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1606271</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n今日香港慘劇係雜種一手造成，冤有頭債有主，請大家對準政權目標<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">有明確訊息證實係習近平一人當日堅持拒絕「撤回」及下令將44人極速起訴暴動！</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1602129\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1602129</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">十一遊行要高叫「天滅中共！習近平全家死」口號落中共面！</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1568634\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1568634</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a6fadb89a4b51f4d89f62a66b6a3f0e4ecdacbd3","tid":1608050,"uid":169392,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T07:11:15.000Z","msg":"香港人！要堅持住！<br />\n黎明前嘅黑暗係最難捱！<br />\n但係再暗再黑都捱過啦，係咪？<br />\n加油呀！<br />\n勇武嘅勇武啲都唔驚！<br />\n我地絕不割蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d62b4ba88950070355c03732f6ecb9a72b11d9e","tid":1608050,"uid":169392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T07:15:23.000Z","msg":"大家頂住呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aca1d5ed70dbe215482a41281cdb63ce40081b2c","tid":1608050,"uid":309753,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T07:15:40.000Z","msg":"絕對唔會割<br />\n壓逼愈大反抗愈大<br />\n所有野都係政權咎由自取"},{"pid":"2e44b09e80744cba7166105da74da3d0da80c314","tid":1608050,"uid":169392,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T07:15:48.000Z","msg":"比多啲人知道你地勇武派唔係炮灰！"},{"pid":"b16c7254f682f6168aebfd1d8cabcfa09d378c48","tid":1608050,"uid":22104,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T07:20:46.000Z","msg":"不割<br />\n勇武唔同我地割, 已經執到"},{"pid":"8d5332ea30bfe284e3dec88eb135315d74e791d1","tid":1608050,"uid":169392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b16c7254f682f6168aebfd1d8cabcfa09d378c48","tid":1